  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "There's a sign that says 'bukubuku tea.'\\nMiku, do you know what that is?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No.\\nTea that's made in Okinawa, maybe?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I think it's a type of tea that bubbles up.\\nIt's named after the drinking method.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "F-Futaro!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Um, I'm...gonna go to a different store!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Ah, Miku?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Kkh...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun...\\nDidn't I tell you that girls are delicate?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Is Miku still being a little too conscious\\nof Fu-kun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Seems that way.\\nWhen she met Futaro-kun just now, she ran away.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Kkh...\\nIn this case, there's only one thing to do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What's that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun...\\nDidn't I tell you not to make that scary face?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It seems like Miku's still really aware\\nof Futaro-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Cause he came at her with such a scary face...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Kkh...\\nIn this case, there's only one thing to do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What's that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "What are you doing, Fu-kun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I wanted to talk to Miku...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "...Ahh, that's what's going on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You say you want to talk, but anyone would run away\\nif you charge at them with such a scary face.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Kkh...\\nIn this case, there's only one thing to do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What's that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "If pushing doesn't work,\\nI'll try pulling her in!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "WHAA%p-2;――%p;?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "No no no!\\nYou shouldn't do that at all!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "That's right!\\nDo you really think you can execute\\nsuch a sophisticated plan?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I-I can do it! Don't underestimate me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun, this isn't the time to be stubborn, is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ooh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Rather, shouldn't you just keep pushing at this time?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Push until I convey how I feel?\\nMeaning, I need to take an offensive approach?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "That's right.\\nYou know the effect it has, don't you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I certainly do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Alright then, I'll go after Miku.\\nSee you later!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}